WEBVTT

00:01.409 --> 00:03.043
You took a case
on contingency

00:03.078 --> 00:05.078
where every plaintiff
is dirt poor.

00:05.113 --> 00:06.046
Dump it.

00:06.081 --> 00:07.747
One of the victims
was my uncle Keith.

00:07.783 --> 00:09.683
Please, these people
need your help.

00:09.718 --> 00:11.818
They need someone like you
to fight for them,

00:11.853 --> 00:13.353
and I can't do it.

00:13.388 --> 00:15.055
Then what do you say
we do it together?

00:15.090 --> 00:16.222
I'd like to propose a change

00:16.258 --> 00:18.124
to the current
compensation formula.

00:18.160 --> 00:19.592
How many partners
do you have in your pocket

00:19.628 --> 00:20.794
if we put your proposal
to a vote?

00:20.829 --> 00:22.262
I can get 45%.

00:22.297 --> 00:23.430
I'm gonna get you
the difference.

00:23.465 --> 00:25.265
This is Harvey's
last three income statements,

00:25.300 --> 00:26.900
and I found them sitting
in the copy machine.

00:26.935 --> 00:28.168
You came to work for me,

00:28.203 --> 00:29.469
so now it's time
for you to decide.

00:29.521 --> 00:30.437
Are you with me or not?

00:30.472 --> 00:32.405
I just called
for a vote tomorrow,

00:32.441 --> 00:34.041
and I hope you've been
saving your money,

00:34.059 --> 00:36.242
because your gravy train's
about to leave the station.

